[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Functional requirements

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
Functional requirements are derived from the system safety requirements
specification and from operational needs. Safety-related requirements are
identified by their traceability to a system safety function. Each requirement
shall be unambiguous, complete, verifiable, and consistent with all other
requirements in this specification.

Duplicate the sample entries SRS-020 and SRS-021 for each function;
remove placeholder text and populate with project-specific content.
