[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Performance and timing requirements

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: SRS-040
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Processing performance requirements
STATEMENT: >>>
The software shall execute within the following performance constraints
under worst-case load and environmental conditions:

  Parameter                | Limit          | Applies to
  -------------------------|----------------|-----------------------------
  Cyclic execution time     | < <n> ms       | All safety-critical tasks
  CPU utilisation (average) | < <n> %        | System under full operational load
  CPU utilisation (peak)    | < <n> %        | Transient peak
  Stack usage               | < <n> % of max | Per-task stack depth
  Memory usage (RAM)        | < <n> %        | Static + dynamic allocation
  Memory usage (ROM/flash)  | < <n> %        | Code + read-only data

Performance shall be verified on the target hardware by measurement under
the worst-case operational scenario defined in the test specification.
<<<
