TITLE: Timing and response time requirements
STATEMENT: >>>
The software shall meet the following timing requirements, derived from
the system-level timing analysis.

  Function / event                | Required response time | Reference
  --------------------------------|------------------------|------------------
  <Safety function 1 response>    | < <n> ms               | System-SRS-<xxx>
  <Safety function 2 response>    | < <n> ms               | System-SRS-<xxx>
  <Watchdog refresh period>       | Every <n> ms           | HW spec §<n>
  <External comms cycle>          | < <n> ms               | IF-EXT-<xx>

All timing requirements shall be verified by worst-case execution time
(WCET) analysis and confirmed by testing on target hardware. The WCET
analysis method and tool shall be specified in the Software Verification Plan.
