The test environment for each test level shall be defined before testing
commences and shall be documented in the applicable test specification.

  Test level | Hardware                  | SW configuration          | Stimuli source
  -----------|---------------------------|---------------------------|------------------
  Level 1    | <Host PC / CI server>     | <Unit test framework>     | <Automated / manual>
  Level 2    | <Host or target board>    | <Integrated modules>      | <Test harness>
  Level 3    | <Target hardware>         | <Full SW, HW interfaces>  | <Test equipment>
