SIL_2: HR
SIL_3: HR
SIL_4: HR
VERIFICATION_METHOD: Inspection, Review
RATIONALE: EN 50716:2023, Clause 7.2 and Table A.1, doc 8 – SRS verification report.

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: SRS-081
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Verification records and verdict
STATEMENT: >>>
The Software Requirements Verification Report shall include:

  - Date and revision of the SRS and test specification reviewed.
  - Name and role of the verifier and independence evidence.
  - Checklist results: each checklist item marked Pass / Fail / N/A
    with observations.
  - List of findings: unique identifier, description, severity
    (Critical / Major / Minor / Observation), and status.
  - Action items raised, with reference to the action item register.
  - Resolution evidence for all Critical and Major findings.
  - Overall verdict: Approved / Approved with conditions / Not approved.

The SRS shall not be baselined and the subsequent design phase shall not
commence until the verification report records an Approved verdict.

